Ian Piumarta's 6502 emulator library.

The source code here is only two files plucked out of the full distro.
To see the whole library, and its documentation, visit:

    http://piumarta.com/software

The original files are in the 'original' folder. These files have been
modified slightly to make them suitable for use in this Lua project (run
'diff' to see the modifications).
